highlights.text: “Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 58 weeks straight.
Migos has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Stir Fry” is the highest at #16.
“Mine” by Bazzi is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 85 spots at #49.
“Narcos” by Migos is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #24.
